  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  singleton pregnancy

          -  gestational age 12-32 weeks

          -  diagnosis of bacterial vaginosis

          -  treatment of bacterial vaginosis with oral clindamycin 300 mg, twice-daily for 7 days

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  multiple pregnancy

          -  allergy to clindamycin
      </textblock>
